Package com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.execution

Contains classes and interfaces responsible for execution of SPRs and high level command by sunrise.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DeviceExecutor.Context
    Implemented by the DeviceExecutor's owner to abstract from the concrete owning class.
    IExecutionContainerStateCallback
    Callback interface that allows to extend the functionality of SunriseExecutionContainer.
    IOverridableRecovery
    Implementations of this interface support a overridable recovery strategy.
    ISPRCommandHook
    Implementing classes may register themselves at a SunriseControllerExecutionService.
    ISPRExecutor
    Capability which executes SPRs on Sunrise controller.
    ISPRExecutorService
    Execution service interface which allows execution of SPRs as controller commands.
    ISPRHook
    Hook that will be called by ISPRExecutor just before it sends SPRs to execution.
    ISPRRuntimeManagementHooks
    Management hooks that can be implemented by classes that can execute SPRs.
    ISPRStateListener
    SPR state listener interface called by the associated SPRRuntime to indicate a SPR state change.
    SPRRuntime.ISPRCancelHook
    Listener which is called if nobody has canceled the SPR so far and the cancel process is started.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeviceExecutor
    Class that executes SPRs for a particular device.
    DeviceMappingSnapshot
    Contains device information that is used at mapping, for example the information needed for setting the reset flag in the spline motion mapping (first motion, stop condition fired etc).
    FiredConditionInfo
    Sunrise implementation of fired condition result.
    MotionContainer
    Represents the state of a motion execution.
    MotionEvents
    Class holding constants for motion events.
    MotionIDSetter
    Listens for a creation of a new SPR-ID in SPRRuntime and sets it in the SplineMotionModule of the Spline Motion SPR.
    MotionSprPrimitive
    Primitive for motion SPRs.
    SplineMotionSprPrimitive
    Primitive class for spline motion SPR which map each motion to a an own spline SPR.
    SPRCommand
    A command wrapping a SPR execution.
    SPRExecutor
    Implementation of SPR executor for Sunrise controller.
    SPRPrimitive
    A primitive consisting of exactly one SPR that has the same life cycle as the Primitive.
    SPRRuntime
    Class managing all runtime issues of the associated SPR.
    SprStack
    Container for a stack of SPRRuntime objects with the following properties: SPRs are added "on top of each other".
    StopConditionType
    StopConditionIndex is defined in Sunrise as follows.
    SunriseControllerExecutionService
    Sunrise execution service.
    SunriseExecutionContainer
    An execution container for Sunrise controller commands.
    SunriseMotionExecutionContainer
    An execution container for Sunrise MOTION controller commands, in other words, this execution container should be used whenever a motion is involved.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    MotionEvents.MotionEvent
    Event that comes from motion (ipo) modules.
    MotionEvents.MotionInfoParams
    Parameters of MOTION_INFO events.
    ResumeMode
    Resume execution modes for sunrise execution service.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    SPRExecutionException
    Exception thrown by ISPRExecutor.executeSPR(com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.api.SPR) when execution of an SPR fails.

Package com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.execution Description

Contains classes and interfaces responsible for execution of SPRs and high level command by sunrise.
This element is an undocumented internal feature. It is not intended to be used by applications as it might change or be removed in future versions.
